reviewText: I only ordered the four pack because I wanted the movie  three movies yet "Serial Mom" and this was all that they had available. I have not watched the other three movies yet, but "Serial Mom" is a hilarious classic! It is satire at its finest and Kathleen Turner is amazing i the title role. I definitely recommend this to anyone who appreciates satire and classic over the top humor.

reviewText: "Serial Mom"is horribly terrific. "Nurse Betty" is the bomb. Great show. "Very Bad Things" is creepy and marvelous. BUT "Your Friends and Neighbors" is a total snoozefest; more like a very boring, slow and unwatchable soap opera. Why was it included on a "dark comedy" compiliation? It is neither dark nor a comedy in any sense. But the other three are great.

reviewText: Of all the value packs this is the best for content and packaging.  2 movies on each disc is a nice feature for this couch potato.I had already seen everything but "Your Friends and Neighbors" but couldn't resist, knowing I would see the others again.  Serial Mom is a classic and very rewatchable.I liked "Friends and Neighbors", which isn't as dark as the others - well, at least, it's not about murder, rather about marital affairs.
